body_html:
Thanks for the bug report!

These messages are benign — I would just ignore them. They won't hurt anything and they only show up if you turn on verbose logging; at worst they could slow down startup a very tiny amount.

We could maybe try to avoid creating op registrations if not building with CUDA, but if it isn't causing a problem I don't think it's a high priority.

However if you want to send a PR to fix it I wouldn't object :-)
